  <h1>Privacy Policy for Conflict Statistic</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> April 29, 2025</p>

  <p><strong>Conflict Statistic</strong> ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our mobile application.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data. We do not require any login, location access, or identity-related permissions.</p>

  <h2>2. Data Sources</h2>
  <p>All the information provided in this app is based on publicly available sources, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Official social media accounts of government bodies</li>
    <li>Open government bulletins</li>
    <li>Verified news outlets</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Our app does <strong>not</strong> use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

